read and write. That's enough. Get your job. Learn 
to be a mechanic or a plumber or go out and work on

31:42.713 --> 31:48.158
construction. And that's what's happening. And 
the first thing you know, the boy's 20 years old, he

31:49.523 --> 31:52.847
gets married, that's it. That's the end of it. And 
then later on, he wants to run for something. He's

31:56.070 --> 31:57.651
not going to get elected, Peter. I mean, it's our 
fault too, you know. We

32:00.454 --> 32:13.808
need people that

32:00.454 --> 32:13.808
will stay here and succeed so that these kids can 
